The Debian Package stellar-captive-core-api
----------------------------

The Captive Stellar-Core API Server can run on a separate machine from Horizon. The server will manage Stellar-Core as a subprocess and provide an HTTP API which Horizon can use remotely to stream ledgers for the purpose of ingestion.

 -- Package Maintainer <packages@stellar.org>  Fri, 16 Oct 2020 13:44:05 +0000
